summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Department of Parks and Recreation; making an appropriation in addition to those authorized by Ordinances 97498, 98859, 99736, 100896, 102017, 103235, 104134, and 104918 from the Park Acquisition and Development Fund for necessary salary and administration expenses in connection with public park and recreation facilities projects contemplated by King County Resolution 34571 and Ordinance 97059.
